Package io.zachohara.github.bukkit.infiniclear

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Executables.InfiniClear
    The implementation for the 'infiniclear' command.
    InfiniClearPlugin
    The InfiniClearPlugin class is the entry point for the plugin.
    WeatherListener
    A WeatherListener listens for changes in the weather of a world, and changes it back to sunshine if protection is enabled.
    WeatherUtil
    The WeatherUtil class contains some useful methods for dealing with weather inside the game.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Executables
    The Executables interface represents the set of commands supported by this plugin, and contains an executable object for each command that acts as the main procedure for the command.
    Rules
    The Rules interface represents the set of commands supported by this plugin, and contains a CommandRulesEntry for each command, which defines information about the expected context of the command.
